 Hausotter führen Schritt für Schritt durch den Forschungsprozess: von der Konzeption über die Datenerhebung und -auswertung bis zu den Ergebnissen. Zudem werden die Potenziale der Methode für die intersektionale Praxisforschung ausgelotet.  afunded by FU Berlin  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0 uhttps://www.degruyter.com/dg/page/open-access-policy  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aEquality. 0aIntersectionality (Sociology). 0aSocial capital (Sociology). 4aEinführung. 4aGender Studies. 4aGeschlecht. 4aGesellschaft. 4aPraxeologie. 4aQualitative Forschung. 4aQualitative Sozialforschung. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Social Classes & Economic Disparity.2bisacsh  aGender Studies.  aGender.  aIntroduction.  aPraxeology.  aQualitative Research.  aQualitative Social Research.  aSocial Inequality.  aSociety.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology.1 aDegele, Nina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHausotter, Jette, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aWinker, Gabriele, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb2 aFU Berlinefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2020 Part 2z978311069629508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Sociology, Education, Psychology 2020z9783110704549oZDB-23-SEW0 cprintz978383764514940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839445143?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839445143zOpen Access70423Cove